---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ReferencePageShell from "../../components/ReferencePageShell.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Knitting Machine Reference | Knit by Machine"
  description="A growing reference of knitting machine models, features, and practical notes."
>
  <ReferencePageShell
    title="Knitting Machine Reference"
    subhead="A growing reference of knitting machine models, features, and practical notes."
    backHref="/learn/reference#category-machine-reference"
    backLabel="Back to Machine References"
  >
    <div class="kbm-intro-callout">
      <p>
        We’re building a detailed reference of knitting machine models,
        including specifications, features, and practical notes gathered
        from years of machine knitting experience.
      </p>

      <p>
        This resource will make it easier to identify machines, understand
        their capabilities, and find helpful information about specific
        models.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>This reference database is currently being prepared and will be available soon.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </ReferencePageShell>
</Layout>